channel.title: How do I make tele commands and Portals go to places?
channel.description:
Well, I'm fairly new to coding. I started to code a server, But I made the starting place near shilo, and when you leave it, you can't get back without memorizing ::tele 2861 2997, and even then you need to be player rights 2 or up. So I wanted to know how to make tele commands, or even emote teles would be fine. Also, I added in portals to get around, The only problem is, I don't know how to get them to go to places.
Help would be useful :(
